归一化和特征提取¶

  • zx_trans：完成数据变换操作，使用小波变换，主要使用sklearn中signal下的cwt变换，小波变换函数使用signal.ricker。
  • find_nearest：查找距离最近的峰，举例不超过nearest默认为100
  • zx_find_peak：找波峰，在[865, 1260,1339,1382,1461,1527, 1661, 2910]几个位置附近查找波峰，波峰最低高度75，最小宽度10。找到的波峰信息写入到数组中返回
  • show_data：可视化信号数据，二维。一般显示原始数据，或小波变换后的数据。
  • show_3d：三位可视化数据，一般显示已经提取完特征的数据，只能显示三个维度，显示三维散点图。
  • all_data_cwt:经过小波变换后的数据，字典格式，整体与all_data格式一致

def zx_trans(df,window_size = 18):
    ds = df.astype(float)
    ds_shift = ds.copy(deep=True)
    w = window_size #定义小波变换的W
    for col in ds.columns:
        x = np.array(ds[col])
        widths = np.arange(1, w)
        cwtmatr = signal.cwt(x, signal.ricker, widths)
        # 可以修改signal.ricker, 使用自定义的函数来修正小波变换
        y = cwtmatr[w-2]
        ds_shift[col] = y
    return ds_shift
def find_nearest(array,value,nearest=50):
    array = np.asarray(array)
    array1 = np.abs(array - value)
    idx = array1.argmin()
    if (array1[idx] < nearest):
        return idx
    else: 
        return -1
def zx_find_peak(ds):
    t = ds
    b,a = signal.butter(2,0.2)
    peak_info = {}
    peaks_list = [865, 1260,1339,1382,1461,1527, 1661, 2910]
    datas = []
    for col,x in t.items():       
        X = signal.filtfilt(b, a, x)
        # 查找宽度不小于10，高度不小于75的峰，峰宽高位置为65%处
        peaks,peaks_dic = signal.find_peaks(X,width=10,prominence=100,rel_height=0.65)
        peak_info[col] = [peaks,peaks_dic]
        t_data = []
        for p in peaks_list:
            idx = find_nearest(peak_info[col][0],p-350)
            if (idx>=0):
                t_data.append([peak_info[col][0][idx]+350,p,peak_info[col][1]['prominences'][idx],peak_info[col][1]['width_heights'][idx]])
            else:
                t_data.append([0,0,0,0])
        datas.append(t_data)
    arr = np.array(datas)
    return arr

def show_data(ds,title='show_data',show_legend=False):
    ax = ds.plot(alpha=0.6,linewidth=0.5,legend=show_legend)
    # ax.set_title("Original Data")
    ax.set_xlabel(r'Raman shift/$\mathrm{cm}^{-1}$',fontsize=14)
    ax.set_ylabel(r'Intensity/a.u.',fontsize=14)
    ax.get_yaxis().set_major_formatter(matplotlib.ticker.FuncFormatter(lambda x, p: format(int(x), ',')))
    x = list(range(200,3400,100))
    ax.set_xticks(x)
    ax.set_xticklabels(x,rotation=75)
    ax.grid(True)
    # ax.get_xaxis().set_major_formatter(matplotlib.ticker.FuncFormatter(lambda x, p: format(int(x), ',')))
    plt.subplots_adjust(left=0.15, right=0.95, top=0.90, bottom=0.15)
    plt.title(title,FontProperties=font,color='red')
    plt.savefig(f"./"+title+".jpg",dpi=1000,format='jpg')
    plt.show()
def show_3d(data1,data2=None,title=''):
    data = pd.DataFrame(data1, columns=['z1','z2','x', 'y']) 
    if (data2 is not None):
        zdata = pd.DataFrame(data2, columns=['z1','z2','x', 'y'])    
    fig = plt.figure()  
    ax = fig.add_subplot(111, projection='3d')    
    ax.scatter(data['x'], data['y'], data['z1']-data['z2'])  
    if data2 is not None:
        ax.scatter(zdata['x'], zdata['y'], zdata['z1']-zdata['z2'],color='red')      
    ax.set_xlabel('峰高',FontProperties=font)  
    ax.set_ylabel('峰宽',FontProperties=font)  
    ax.set_zlabel('位置',FontProperties=font)  
    plt.title(title,FontProperties=font)
    plt.savefig(f"./show_3d_"+title+".jpg",dpi=600,format='jpg')
    plt.show()

def prepro_data(data):
    arr_3d = data.copy()
    arr_3d[:,:,0] = arr_3d[:,:,0] - arr_3d[:,:,1]
    arr_3d = np.delete(arr_3d, 1,axis=2)        
    arr_2d = arr_3d.reshape(arr_3d.shape[0],-1)
    return StandardScaler().fit_transform(arr_2d)

from sklearn.cluster import SpectralClustering  
from sklearn.neighbors import NearestNeighbors  
import numpy as np  
def cluster_metrics(cla_id,show_ans=False,n_clusters=3) :  
# 假设X是待聚类的样本数据 
    X = None
    if isinstance(cla_id,list):
        for cla in cla_id:
            t = prepro_data(all_data_sift[cla])
            if X is not None:
                X = np.concatenate((X,t),axis=0)
            else:
                X = t.copy()
    else: 
        X = prepro_data(all_data_sift[cla_id])
    print(X.shape)
    # 使用SpectralClustering进行聚类  
    spectral = SpectralClustering(n_clusters=n_clusters, affinity='nearest_neighbors').fit(X)  
    
    # 获取聚类标签  
    labels = spectral.labels_  
    
    # 计算每个样本的离散程度  
    y_pred = spectral.labels_.astype(int)
    silhouetee_avg = silhouette_score(X, y_pred)
    cal_avg = calinski_harabasz_score(X,y_pred)
    DB_avg = davies_bouldin_score(X,y_pred)
    
    stds = []  
    for i in range(X.shape[0]):  
        # 找到同簇的样本索引  
        cluster_indices = np.where(labels == labels[i])[0]  
        # 计算样本之间的平均距离  
        distances = np.mean(np.sqrt(np.sum((X[cluster_indices] - X[i]) ** 2, axis=1)))  
        # 计算样本与不同簇样本之间的平均距离（使用最近邻搜索）  
        distances_to_other_clusters = []  
        for j in range(X.shape[0]):  
            if j != i and labels[j] != i:  
                distances_to_other_clusters.append(np.sqrt(np.sum((X[i] - X[j]) ** 2)))  
        distances_to_other_clusters = np.mean(distances_to_other_clusters)  
        # 计算离散程度指标  
        std = distances / distances_to_other_clusters  
        stds.append(std)  
    if show_ans:
        # print(cla_id,'\n',labels)
        print(cla_id)
        for i in range(n_clusters):
            print(i,':',np.count_nonzero(labels == i),end=' | ')
        # print(np.argpartition(stds,5)[:])
        # print(np.argsort(stds))
        print(f"\n轮廓系数：{silhouetee_avg}  方差比标准 CHI：{cal_avg} DB指数：{DB_avg} ")
        # for i in range(len(stds)):
        #     print(f" {i:02d}: {stds[i]:.3f}",end=' ')
        #     if i % 10 ==9:
        #         print()
    return (labels,stds,silhouetee_avg,cal_avg,DB_avg)

class_key = {'g':0,'k':2,'z':1}
import random
def set_class(class_list,class_label,col_train,col_test):
    y_train = []
    y_test =[]
    for c in class_list: 
        sample_n = all_data_cwt[c].shape[1]
        sample = list(all_data_cwt[c].columns)
        random.shuffle(sample)
        n = int(all_data_cwt[c].shape[1]*0.8)
        class_count[c] = (n,sample_n-n)
        for i in sample[:n]:
            col_train.append(i)
        for i in sample[n:]:
            col_test.append(i)
        y_train = y_train+[class_label]*n
        y_test = y_test +[class_label]*(sample_n-n)
    return (y_train,y_test)

机器学习常用方法进行分类实验¶

数据准备¶

通过提取到的特征，我们可以将数据集分为训练集和测试集。训练集用于训练模型，测试集用于评估模型的性能。

In [ ]:
from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split
# 分割样本集，得到训练集和测试集
ml_x = []
ml_y = []
class_key = {'g':0,'k':2,'z':1}
for id in all_data_sift.keys():
    # print(id,all_data_sift[id].shape)
    for emp in all_data_sift[id]:
        ml_x.append(np.reshape(emp,(1,-1))[0])
        ml_y.append(class_key[id[0]])
ml_x = np.array(ml_x)
ml_y = np.array(ml_y)
print(ml_x.shape,ml_y.shape)
ml_x_train,ml_x_test,ml_y_train,ml_y_test = train_test_split(ml_x,ml_y,test_size=0.2,random_state=0)
print(ml_x_train.shape,ml_y_train.shape,ml_x_test.shape,ml_y_test.shape)

(661, 32) (661,)
(528, 32) (528,) (133, 32) (133,)

from sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression

def set_array(X,new_size):
    temp = []
    for i in range(len(X)):
        temp.append(np.reshape(X[i],new_size))
    return np.array(temp)

import pandas as pd 
import numpy as np 
from torch.utils.data import Dataset, DataLoader 
from torchvision import datasets, transforms
# 自定义Dataset的子类 
class MyDataset(Dataset): 
    # 构造器初始化方法 
    def __init__(self, data_X, data_y): 
        self.data_X = data_X
        self.data_y = data_y 
    # 重写getitem方法用于通过idx获取数据内容 
    def __getitem__(self, idx): 
        return self.data_X[idx], self.data_y[idx] 
    # 重写len方法获取数据集大小 
    def __len__(self): 
        return self.data_X.shape[0] 
# 构造Dataset对象 
train_data = MyDataset(train_data_x, y_train)

定义胶囊网络结构¶

In [ ]:
from __future__ import print_function

# pytorch 
import torch
# 神经网络
import torch.nn as nn
# 神经网络中的常用函数，包括卷积函数，polling函数，激活函数，损失函数，啥函数都有
import torch.nn.functional as F  
# 数学包
import math
# 实现各种优化算法的软件包，lr_scheduler提供了几种方法，用于根据纪元数调整学习速率
from torch.optim import lr_scheduler
# 提供实现任意标量值函数自动分化的类和函数。它需要对现有代码进行最小的更改 - 您只需要声明 s，应使用关键字计算梯度。
from torch.autograd import Variable

# 胶囊网络的一大创新，全新的非线性激活函数，接受一个向量，然后再不改变方向的前提下，压缩他的长度到1一下，相当于向量的归一化

def squash(x):
    lengths2 = x.pow(2).sum(dim=2)
    lengths = lengths2.sqrt()
    x = x * (lengths2 / (1 + lengths2) / lengths).view(x.size(0), x.size(1), 1)
    return x


class AgreementRouting(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, input_caps, output_caps, n_iterations):
        super(AgreementRouting, self).__init__()
        self.n_iterations = n_iterations
        self.b = nn.Parameter(torch.zeros((input_caps, output_caps)))

    def forward(self, u_predict):
        batch_size, input_caps, output_caps, output_dim = u_predict.size()

        c = F.softmax(self.b)
        s = (c.unsqueeze(2) * u_predict).sum(dim=1)
        v = squash(s)

        if self.n_iterations > 0:
            b_batch = self.b.expand((batch_size, input_caps, output_caps))
            for r in range(self.n_iterations):
                v = v.unsqueeze(1)
                b_batch = b_batch + (u_predict * v).sum(-1)

                c = F.softmax(b_batch.view(-1, output_caps)).view(-1, input_caps, output_caps, 1)
                s = (c * u_predict).sum(dim=1)
                v = squash(s)

        return v

# 路由胶囊层，用于编码空间信息并进行最终分类
class CapsLayer(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, input_caps, input_dim, output_caps, output_dim, routing_module):
        super(CapsLayer, self).__init__()
        self.input_dim = input_dim
        self.input_caps = input_caps
        self.output_dim = output_dim
        self.output_caps = output_caps
        self.weights = nn.Parameter(torch.Tensor(input_caps, input_dim, output_caps * output_dim))
        self.routing_module = routing_module
        self.reset_parameters()

    def reset_parameters(self):
        stdv = 1. / math.sqrt(self.input_caps)
        self.weights.data.uniform_(-stdv, stdv)

    def forward(self, caps_output):
        caps_output = caps_output.unsqueeze(2)
        u_predict = caps_output.matmul(self.weights)
        u_predict = u_predict.view(u_predict.size(0), self.input_caps, self.output_caps, self.output_dim)
        v = self.routing_module(u_predict)
        return v

# 初始胶囊层，用于第二次卷积并初始化胶囊输入
class PrimaryCapsLayer(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, input_channels, output_caps, output_dim, kernel_size, stride):
        # input_channels 输入通道, output_caps 输出胶囊, output_dim 输出维度, kernel_size 卷积核大小, stride 步幅
        super(PrimaryCapsLayer, self).__init__()
        self.conv = nn.Conv2d(input_channels, output_caps * output_dim, kernel_size=kernel_size, stride=stride)
        self.input_channels = input_channels
        self.output_caps = output_caps
        self.output_dim = output_dim

    def forward(self, input):
        out = self.conv(input)
        N, C, H, W = out.size()
        out = out.view(N, self.output_caps, self.output_dim, H, W)

        # will output N x OUT_CAPS x OUT_DIM
        # premute()进行tensor张量的维度变换 permute(0, 1, 3, 4, 2) 表示将第三个维度 换到了最后一个维度，其他维度一次向前，正常的维度变换
        # 只是修改了标识，新旧tensor还是回共享内存，利用contiguous()函数完成深度复制，这样能得到全新的tensor
        # 本层的各种复杂操作完全是为了卷积之后，数据变换，改变数据的形状
        out = out.permute(0, 1, 3, 4, 2).contiguous()
        out = out.view(out.size(0), -1, out.size(4))
        out = squash(out)
        return out

# 胶囊网络，主要是三层，卷积层，初始胶囊层，路由胶囊层
class CapsNet(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, routing_iterations, n_classes=3):
        super(CapsNet, self).__init__()
        
        self.conv1 = nn.Conv2d(1, 256, kernel_size=9, stride=1)   #卷积层
        self.primaryCaps = PrimaryCapsLayer(256, 32, 8, kernel_size=9, stride=2)  # outputs 6*6  初始胶囊层
        self.num_primaryCaps = 32 * 6 * 6
        routing_module = AgreementRouting(self.num_primaryCaps, n_classes, routing_iterations)   # 动态路由层
        self.digitCaps = CapsLayer(self.num_primaryCaps, 8, n_classes, 16, routing_module)  # 路由胶囊层

    def forward(self, input):
        x = self.conv1(input)
        x = F.relu(x)
        x = self.primaryCaps(x)
        x = self.digitCaps(x)
        probs = x.pow(2).sum(dim=2).sqrt()
        return x, probs


class ReconstructionNet(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, n_dim=16, n_classes=10):
        super(ReconstructionNet, self).__init__()
        self.fc1 = nn.Linear(n_dim * n_classes, 512)
        self.fc2 = nn.Linear(512, 1024)
        self.fc3 = nn.Linear(1024, 784)
        self.n_dim = n_dim
        self.n_classes = n_classes

    def forward(self, x, target):
        mask = Variable(torch.zeros((x.size()[0], self.n_classes)), requires_grad=False)
        if next(self.parameters()).is_cuda:
            mask = mask.cuda()
        mask.scatter_(1, target.view(-1, 1), 1.)
        mask = mask.unsqueeze(2)
        x = x * mask
        x = x.view(-1, self.n_dim * self.n_classes)
        x = F.relu(self.fc1(x))
        x = F.relu(self.fc2(x))
        x = F.sigmoid(self.fc3(x))
        return x


class CapsNetWithReconstruction(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, capsnet, reconstruction_net):
        super(CapsNetWithReconstruction, self).__init__()
        self.capsnet = capsnet
        self.reconstruction_net = reconstruction_net

    def forward(self, x, target):
        x, probs = self.capsnet(x)
        reconstruction = self.reconstruction_net(x, target)
        return reconstruction, probs


class MarginLoss(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, m_pos, m_neg, lambda_):
        super(MarginLoss, self).__init__()
        self.m_pos = m_pos
        self.m_neg = m_neg
        self.lambda_ = lambda_

    def forward(self, lengths, targets, size_average=True):
        t = torch.zeros(lengths.size()).long()
        if targets.is_cuda:
            t = t.cuda()
        t = t.scatter_(1, targets.data.view(-1, 1), 1)
        targets = Variable(t)
        losses = targets.float() * F.relu(self.m_pos - lengths).pow(2) + \
                 self.lambda_ * (1. - targets.float()) * F.relu(lengths - self.m_neg).pow(2)
        return losses.mean() if size_average else losses.sum()

# import argparse
import torch.optim as optim
from torchvision import datasets, transforms
from torch.autograd import Variable
# torch.manual_seed(1)
torch.cuda.manual_seed(1)
model = CapsNet(3)
model.cuda()
optimizer = optim.Adam(model.parameters(), lr=0.00001)
scheduler = lr_scheduler.ReduceLROnPlateau(optimizer, verbose=True, patience=15, min_lr=1e-7)
loss_fn = MarginLoss(0.9, 0.1, 0.7)
def train(epoch,show_detail):
    model.train()
    for batch_idx, (data, target) in enumerate(train_loader):   
        data = data.type(torch.FloatTensor)    
        data, target = data.cuda(), target.cuda() 
        data, target = Variable(data), Variable(target, requires_grad=False)
        optimizer.zero_grad()        
        output, probs = model(data)
        loss = loss_fn(probs, target)
        loss.backward()
        optimizer.step()
def test(show_detail):
    model.eval()
    test_loss = 0
    correct = 0
    for data, target in test_loader:   
        data = data.type(torch.FloatTensor)
        data, target = data.cuda(), target.cuda()
        data, target = Variable(data, volatile=True), Variable(target)
        output, probs = model(data)
        test_loss += loss_fn(probs, target, size_average=False).data
        pred = probs.data.max(1, keepdim=True)[1] 
        correct += pred.eq(target.data.view_as(pred)).cpu().sum()
    test_loss /= len(test_loader.dataset)
    if show_detail :
        print('Test set: Average loss: {:.4f}, Accuracy: {}/{} ({:.0f}%)\n'.format(
            test_loss, correct, len(test_loader.dataset),
            100. * correct / len(test_loader.dataset)))
    return (test_loss,100. * correct / len(test_loader.dataset))
def test_train(show_detail):
    model.eval()
    test_loss = 0
    correct = 0
    for data, target in train_loader:   
        data = data.type(torch.FloatTensor)
        data, target = data.cuda(), target.cuda()
        data, target = Variable(data, volatile=True), Variable(target)
        output, probs = model(data)
        test_loss += loss_fn(probs, target, size_average=False).data
        pred = probs.data.max(1, keepdim=True)[1] 
        correct += pred.eq(target.data.view_as(pred)).cpu().sum()
    test_loss /= len(train_loader.dataset)
    if show_detail:
        print('Test train_data set: Average loss: {:.4f}, Accuracy: {}/{} ({:.0f}%)\n'.format(
            test_loss, correct, len(train_loader.dataset),
            100. * correct / len(train_loader.dataset)))
    return (test_loss,100. * correct / len(train_loader.dataset))

acc_list = []
train_acc_list = []
lose_list = []
train_loss_list = []
for epoch in range(1, 300 + 1):
    show_detail = (epoch % 10 ==0)
    train(epoch,show_detail)
    if show_detail:
        print(epoch,':',end=' ')
    test_loss,Accuracy = test(show_detail)
    train_loss,train_acc = test_train(show_detail)
    scheduler.step(test_loss)
    acc_list.append(Accuracy)
    train_acc_list.append(train_acc)
    lose_list.append(test_loss)
    train_loss_list.append(train_loss)
    if (Accuracy>=80):
        torch.save(model.state_dict(),
                    '{:03d}_model_dict.pth'.format(epoch))

def prob_data(show_detail,id='test'):
    if (id != 'test'):
        data = torch.tensor(train_data_x)
        target = torch.tensor(y_train)
        col_list = col_train
    else:
        data = torch.tensor(test_data_x)
        target = torch.tensor(y_test)
        col_list = col_test
    del_col = []
    data = data.type(torch.FloatTensor)
    data, target = data.cuda(), target.cuda()
    data, target = Variable(data, volatile=True), Variable(target)
    output, probs = model(data)
    pred = probs.data.max(1, keepdim=True)[1] 
    ans = pred.eq(target.view_as(pred)).cuda().flatten().tolist()
    for i in range(len(ans)):
        if (ans[i]==False) :
            del_col.append(col_list[i])
    return (pred.flatten().tolist(),ans,del_col)
